{"tid":1808950,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"(特種部隊心法)如何忍受嚴刑拷問","createTime":"2020-01-02T17:23:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-04T14:08:03.000Z","uid":54303,"like":61,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"72a2515076cebee37df316178ea0264e82624dfe","tid":1808950,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T17:23:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=A-crl3_C3Ko&amp;feature=emb_logo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DA-crl3_C3Ko%26feature%3Demb_logo&d=lD%2FUaJpd7HswZ4lFnFCcPh9HEPLFM%2Fpg3GuXTgQF%2FE0%3D&h=6cc1abee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=A-crl3_C3Ko&amp;feature=emb_logo</a><br />\n<br />\n影片重點:<br />\n1. 拷問者想摧殘你既身心, 攻擊你既尊嚴同人格, 要有心理準備會被羞辱&amp;滋擾<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2. 絕對唔可以透露不必要資訊, 更加唔好簽任何野</span><br />\n3. 不卑不亢, 唔好串嘴亦唔好淆底, 保持冷靜<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">4. 注意自己既眼神, 唔小心郁一郁都可以出賣你諗緊乜</span> (可以係屋企練習下)<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">5. 佢地絕對唔係你既朋友, 請你保持戒心, 唔好真心相信佢地任何既「善意」</span> <br />\n6. 唔好比佢了解你既為人, <span style=\"color: red;\">你既任何潛在弱點都會被呢班敵人利用</span><br />\n7. 如果真係逼不得已要講野, 唔好透露全部真相, 講一半真一半假, 或者只係講一部份 (當然, 比佢捉到你玩佢就麻煩, 所以出聲之前諗定乜野可以講)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果你想知道更多, 可以去google搵&quot;Resistance to interrogation&quot;, 了解更多軍人既反拷問訓練方法"},{"pid":"21705b6b04252403b3fa3c9e0435b46d3b65a1ba","tid":1808950,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T17:24:47.000Z","msg":"求求大家比有需要/有興趣既朋友睇睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a518a54efb5f48e65d56bb0ff716889bb66e3107","tid":1808950,"uid":176460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T17:25:15.000Z","msg":"【戰術】【快做仆街仔】大量珍藏流出！新年送大禮！！勁過除夕抽獎！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1808752\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1808752</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"046024efa52c111773fb022c74eb46af53bd7f05","tid":1808950,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":